ragnarok-installer (01-4) stable; urgency=medium

  * New feature: allow users to install custom sets or deb pkgs.
  * Bug fixes:
    * Fixed a bug that messed up disk creation if Rootpass is also
      present in install.conf.
    * Fixed wrong path for /var/messages in afterinstall.
    * Multiple small fixes.

